{
  "stem": "24409.10",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And sergeant comes in, you come in, or the PFC comes in and looks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was one of the last bunks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he looks at the bunk and goes [? throws it-- ?] he throws it all into air.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Air.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, ?] we can help this then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He will assign somebody to make the bunk for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I told him-- I didn't tell him, but I went to the, to the, to the [INAUDIBLE], to the military intelligence section.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told them, and they shipped me-- they asked me-- they tested languages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was, there was, a man there, he said, speak Italian?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a [? second ?] guy who was with, with me with all the European Jews speak Italian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He spoke a little bit of Italian, but he mixed it up with words which sounded Italian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Speaks French.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I speak French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He spoke a few French words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew a little French, but German he spoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were both shipped to the military intelligence training center in [INAUDIBLE] [? in Maryland. ?] And yeah, after I went through the military intelligence training school for 12 weeks, which was very good, gave me very much.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could learn a lot there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only they fed you so much that you couldn't learn it all what they gave you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was 12 weeks from, actually, the mornings until 6:00, or 5:00 in the afternoon, with half an hour, or an hour, lunch break.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they stuffed in you, but I made out all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was through with this, this training, I went to the chapel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted to get to the general and tell him that they could use my handwriting knowledge for military intelligence purposes.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
